results.name: Inverse permutation to sequence A014631.
link: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
mathematica: lst = {1}; t = Flatten[Table[Binomial[n, m], {n, 16}, {m, Floor[n/2]}]]; Do[ If[ !MemberQ[lst, t[[n]]], AppendTo[lst, t[[n]] ]], {n, Length@t}]; Flatten@Table[ Position[lst, n], {n, 61}] (* _Robert G. Wilson v_ *)
